name: Pet Runner
summary: Get ready for the ultimate running adventure in Pet Runner! Choose your favorite pet and sprint through vibrant landscapes filled with challenges and surprises. Dodge obstacles, gather coins, and unlock powerful upgrades to enhance your gameplay. Customize your pet’s appearance with unique outfits and accessories, adding a personal touch to every run.  Pet Runner offers fast-paced gameplay that’s engaging and easy to pick up, while still providing dynamic challenges to keep you coming back for more.
